column5:
40 pages, revised and mildly reorganized to reflect referee feedback;
  a subsection before the conclusion outlining a simplicial sets perspective on
  these partition principles has been added as well

25 pages in World Scientific LaTeX style, 21 eps figures, 1 table;
  text is revised significantly, several new references are added, version
  published in Int.J.Mod.Phys.D
